{
  "info": {
    "name": "Financial Gateway - Simulation API",
    "description": "API para simulación de créditos con validación de políticas crediticias y comparación entre bancos (Bancolombia, Davivienda, Coltefinanciera) usando n8n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "gateway_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8090",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "n8n_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5678",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Credit Simulation",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Simulation - Success (Good Credit Profile)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"USR001\",\n  \"amount\": 10000000,\n  \"termMonths\": 24,\n  \"monthlyIncome\": 5000000\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/api/simulation",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "simulation"]
            },
            "description": "✅ Usuario con buen perfil crediticio (ingresos altos, monto razonable, plazo adecuado)\n\nEspera recibir:\n- success: true\n- 3 ofertas aprobadas de todos los bancos\n- bestOffer con la mejor opción\n- savings mostrando cuánto ahorra vs segunda mejor oferta"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Simulation - Rejected (Low Income)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"USR002\",\n  \"amount\": 15000000,\n  \"termMonths\": 12,\n  \"monthlyIncome\": 2000000\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/api/simulation",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "simulation"]
            },
            "description": "❌ Usuario con bajo perfil crediticio (bajos ingresos para monto alto)\n\nEspera recibir:\n- success: false\n- message: 'Simulation rejected due to credit policies'\n- allOffers con razones de rechazo de cada banco\n- policyRejected: true\n- codCausal con código de causal de rechazo"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Simulation - Invalid Amount (Too Low)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"USR003\",\n  \"amount\": 500000,\n  \"termMonths\": 24,\n  \"monthlyIncome\": 3000000\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/api/simulation",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "simulation"]
            },
            "description": "⚠️ Validación del Gateway - Monto fuera de rango (< 1M)\n\nEspera recibir:\n- success: false\n- message: 'Invalid request parameters'\n- reason: 'Amount out of range (1M - 50M)'\n\nNota: Esta validación ocurre ANTES de llamar a n8n"
          },
          "response": []
